# 6. 想いがつなぐ出会い

Miku: Where are we...?
KAITO: This could be another SEKAI born out of someone's feelings.
Rin: Which means that thing had to be a fragment of a feeling! But what feelings was this SEKAI born from?
MEIKO: I'm not sure, but look... I think I see each of the others' SEKAI among all these floating fragments.
Len: Whoa, you're right...! Does this mean we can peer into a bunch of different SEKAI from this SEKAI?
Luka: Possibly. For now, let's try to learn more about where we are.
KAITO: Right. It looks extremely expansive, so why don't we split up to cover more ground...?
Rin: Okay! See you guys later!
MEIKO: This SEKAI is so strange...
MEIKO: Not only is our SEKAI visible from inside a fragment, but I can see all these other ones as well.
Rin: Yeah...
Rin: I thought this might be another person's SEKAI at first... But I guess it's not.
MEIKO: Why do you say that?
Rin: I mean, who would know this many SEKAI?
???: Huh? That looks like...
Rin: What?
Rin: Oh, I knew it! Hi, me!
Rin: Wait, uhh...
Rin: This is so amazing! I wasn't sure if this was actually possible!
Rin: I've been watching you this whole time!
Rin: You've been watching me...?
Rin: Yeah! The way you express yourself through singing is so great! And you have such a beautiful voice!
Rin: No, I'm really not that great a...
Rin: Don't say that! I know you're doing your best for everyone, so I'm gonna keep rooting for you!
Rin: Oh...
Rin: Oh, since we're here together like this, let's sing!
Rin: I bet we'd sound amazing if we sang together right now!
Rin: Okay...
MEIKO: Hehe. Rin certainly seems excited.
MEIKO: ...
MEIKO: Thank you for being such a strong source of support for the others.
MEIKO: All we can do is watch over them, but I can see that they're in good hands!
MEIKO: I haven't really done anything for them...
MEIKO: Rin and the others are the ones who help them.
MEIKO: Oh? I think you've done plenty for them already.
MEIKO: I have...?
MEIKO: Yes! Based on what I've seen watching you all this time, it's obvious to me that they need you.
MEIKO: You don't always have to put what you feel into words. They feel better just knowing that you're there for them.
MEIKO: So, again, thank you!
KAITO: M-Me?! But how...?!
KAITO: I'm not sure either. I just ended up in this SEKAI for some reason...
KAITO: Oh, that also happened to me. Still... Hmm...
KAITO: Is something wrong?
KAITO: No, it's just... I look... I mean, you look so cool!
KAITO: I'm still not sure how I got here, but it's really great to meet you!
KAITO: Ahaha...
KAITO: I feel the same way. It's nice to meet you.
KAITO: This gives me an opportunity to thank you for doing what you can for the others.
KAITO: What?
KAITO: Your cheerful personality and the way you freely express yourself through words and music have been an enormous source of support for them.
KAITO: So, thank you very much.
Len: I've been wanting to meet you for the longest time! You're such a great guitarist, you're mature and you're so cool!
Len: Cool? Me...?
Len: Yeah! You were just having guitar practice, right? It's super cool how you're trying to pull everyone forward through your singing and playing!
Len: Y-You think so...?
Len: I know so! Which is why I also need to do better!
Len: So, let's both do our best!
Len: Yeah, let's...!
Luka: It's so wonderful how you're able to spread so much hope as an idol.
Luka: And you shine so brightly each time you take the stage. I get a huge boost of encouragement whenever I see you perform...
Luka: I'm a source of encouragement for you?
Luka: Hehe. Thank you so much...!
Luka: I'll put your words to good use by shining even brighter moving forward.
Miku: Wow...! Are you me?! Is this really happening?!
Miku: Hehe. Yes, I'm really here!
Miku: I've been watching what you've been doing for so long!
Miku: The shows you put on are always so fun and exciting. It's wonderful how they put smiles on everyone's faces.
Miku: You've seen my shows?!
Miku: I have! They always fill me with so much hope and joy!
Miku: Which is also why I know that you've been doing your best to support the others.
Miku: ...!
Miku: Even if they get stuck or run into a problem that they don't know how to solve in the future...
Miku: I'm sure they'll be fine! Because I know you'll be there to help them!
Miku: So, keep up the good work!
Miku: Okay!
Miku: Now, can you tell me more about yourself?! I wanna learn more about this me I don't know☆
Miku: Hehe. I see. Then...
Miku: Oh... I think this SEKAI is about to disappear.
Miku: What?! But I wanna keep chatting...
Miku: Me too. After finally getting a chance to meet you...
Miku: Wait, before we have to go! There's something I need to ask you!
Miku: Ask me?
Miku: Yeah, um!
Miku: When I was practicing for my next show just now, I heard someone say, “You can do it!”
Miku: Was that...?!
Miku: Yes! That was me!
Miku: I was cheering you all on so that you can keep doing your best for the others!
Miku: Thanks!
